original_title: Boogie Beebies - Move Your Feet to the Beat
overview: Episodes featured include: 'Shoe Hoedown', 'Going to the Park', 'Penguin Bop', 'Double Decker', 'Building', 'Tick Tock Clock', 'Carousel', 'Do the Duck' and 'Chuffa Chuffa Chawoowoo'.
tagline: Another volume of dancing fun from the CBBC show, with all sorts of dancing games for young children.
title: Boogie Beebies - Move Your Feet to the Beat
